OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1772730671
OL,3,CBritons stranded across the Middle
OL,4,CEast as US strikes on Iran continue
OL,6,FAround 300,000 British nationals are
OL,7,Fstranded in Gulf Arab states, as major
OL,8,Finternational airports including
OL,9,FDubai's remain closed following
OL,10,Fmissile strikes across the region.
OL,12,FIran has continued to fire missiles at
OL,13,Fits neighbours following US and
OL,14,FIsraeli airstrikes on the country,
OL,15,Fwhich hit Tehran and killed Iran's
OL,16,FSupreme Leader, Ali Khamenei.
OL,18,FFlights to and from countries in the
OL,19,FMiddle East are to remain suspended as
OL,20,Fthe conflict in the region continues,
OL,21,Fmajor airlines have said.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
