PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1772730671
OL,3,CBritons stranded across the Middle
OL,4,CEast as US strikes on Iran continue
OL,6,FDubai is a particularly popular
OL,7,Fholiday destination for Brits, while
OL,8,Fpeople many across our region will
OL,9,Fhave family or friends who live and
OL,10,Fwork in the United Arab Emirates (UAE)
OL,11,Fand Bahrain.
OL,13,F102,000 Britons had registered their
OL,14,Fpresence in the Middle East with the
OL,15,FUK Government by Monday morning, with
OL,16,Fmost of these people currently in the
OL,17,FUAE.
OL,19,FJack Crowe from the Scottish Borders
OL,20,Fwas on holiday in Dubai when the
OL,21,Fmissile attacks began.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1772730671
OL,3,CBritons stranded across the Middle
OL,4,CEast as US strikes on Iran continue
OL,6,FHe told ITV Border: "The only thing
OL,7,Fthat's affecting us are the flights -
OL,8,Fthere are so many people stuck here
OL,9,Fand there's a massive backlog.
OL,11,F"There's no sense of panic, no people
OL,12,Frunning about. It seems very
OL,13,Fcontrolled, which is really reassuring.
OL,15,F"When it started we were just lying on
OL,16,Fthe beach and we heard the explosions
OL,17,Fgoing off. But no-one ran in panic or
OL,18,Fanything like that."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
