PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1772730671
OL,3,CBritons stranded across the Middle
OL,4,CEast as US strikes on Iran continue
OL,6,FThe closure of Dubai International
OL,7,FAirport - the world's busiest - has
OL,8,Fhad an impact on flights across the
OL,9,Fglobe, with major routes using the
OL,10,Fairport for connections.
OL,12,FDavid, a music manager from Kendal,
OL,13,Fwas due to fly from Stockholm to Cape
OL,14,FTown via Dubai on Saturday. His flight
OL,15,Fwas cancelled around 90 minutes before
OL,16,Fits scheduled departure.
OL,18,FDavid told ITV Border: "I have been
OL,19,Flucky as I have the time to extend my
OL,20,Ftrip by a couple of days in Cape Town
OL,21,Fand have only been delayed by 2 days.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1772730671
OL,3,CBritons stranded across the Middle
OL,4,CEast as US strikes on Iran continue
OL,6,F"I would rather be safe in Sweden than
OL,7,Fdodging missiles in Dubai."
OL,9,FDavid has now rebooked with a
OL,10,Fdifferent airline and via a different
OL,11,Froute to reach Cape Town.
OL,13,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper told
OL,14,FITV News on the morning of Monday
OL,15,FMarch 2: "Where airspace is now closed
OL,16,Fwe're asking people to register their
OL,17,Fpresence with the Foreign Office. That
OL,18,Fmeans we know where people are and
OL,19,Falso can provide people with updated
OL,20,Fadvice and information.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1772730671
OL,3,CBritons stranded across the Middle
OL,4,CEast as US strikes on Iran continue
OL,6,F"We're working closely with airlines,
OL,7,Ftravel agencies, and with the
OL,8,Fgovernments in the region to ensure
OL,9,Fpeople can travel safely home. But at
OL,10,Fthe moment we are urging people to
OL,11,Ffollow the local advice to shelter in
OL,12,Fplace.
OL,14,F"This is an unprecedented situation.
OL,15,FWe're sending rapid deployment teams
OL,16,Fto the region to work with our
OL,17,Fembassies and consular teams in order
OL,18,Fto be able to plan.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1772730671
OL,3,CBritons stranded across the Middle
OL,4,CEast as US strikes on Iran continue
OL,6,F"The faster that airspace can be
OL,7,Freopened the better. We are working at
OL,8,Fpace to look through all the possible
OL,9,Foptions to make sure that people can
OL,10,Fsafely return home."
OL,12,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,13,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,14,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,15,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/7
